      "rationale": "Standard patch test and cantilever beam benchmark cases executed in Ansys Mechanical R2023 yield results within 0.2% of analytical solutions. Contact mechanics benchmark (Hertzian sphere-on-flat) matches analytical prediction within 0.4%. Code verification requirements satisfied at required level 2."
